  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p>You store a misterious energy while rotating both arms, then shoot it forward on an unsuspecting creature within range. Make a melee Genjutsu attack, dealing 6d10 psychic damage and forcing the target to make an intelligence saving throw:</p><ul><li><strong>Critical Success</strong>: no damage or effect.</li><li><strong>Success</strong>: The target becomes confused until the end of their next turn.</li><li><strong>Failure</strong>: The target becomes dazed and confused until the end of their next turn.</li><li><strong>Critical Failure</strong>: As a failure, but the target becomes dazed and confused for 1 minute. A creature can repeat their saving throw at the end of each of their turns, ending this genjutsu on itself on a success.</li></ul><p><strong>At higher ranks:</strong> For each rank above B-rank, increase this jutsu's cost by 3 and the damage by 1d10. Starting at A-rank, this jutsu becomes <strong>Grand Dark Jade Fist</strong>, and forces all creatures within 10ft of the target (other than you) to make the intelligence saving throw.</p>",
